feedback_group.textSpeak: Turn on the External Power to give us the electrical power.
Turn on batteries 1 and 2.

feedback_group.adviceText: Turn on MASTER SWITCH in APU.
feedback_group.textSpeak: Turn the APU Master switch on to start the engines.
Turn the APU Start switch on.
Turn on the APU Generator to give the airplane the electrical power without external assistance.
Turn off the External Power, since we don't need it anymore.
Turn on the APU BLEED.

feedback_group.adviceText: Set on all the following fuel's PUMPS:
feedback_group.textSpeak: Set on all the fuel's Pumps.
Set the Engines Switch to the value 'START'.
Switch the engines master 1 and 2 to start the respective engines.

feedback_group.adviceText: Wait until the engines reach the value 30% on the monitor.
feedback_group.textSpeak: Now wait the engines to spool up to 30%, so that they become responsive.
Switch the Engine Switch back to the value 'NORM'.
Turn on the engine generators 1 and 2.
Turn off the APU BLEED.
Turn on Pack 1 and Pack 2.
Since we are generating electrical power through the engines, turn off the APU Generator, APU Start and APU Master switches.
Release the parking brake.

feedback_group.adviceText: Set the Auto Brake to MAX.
feedback_group.textSpeak: Set the Auto Brake to MAX.
Set the spoiler armed.
Set the flaps to 1.
Turn off Pack 1 and Pack 2.

feedback_group.adviceText: Full in the Throttles to apply full power.
feedback_group.textSpeak: Full in the Throttles to apply full power.

feedback_group.adviceText: Wait until the airplane gains sufficient speed.
feedback_group.textSpeak: Wait until the airplane gains sufficient speed.

feedback_group.adviceText: Pull back the yoke to take off. Go up until you reach 500 foot.
feedback_group.textSpeak: Pull back the yoke to take off. Go up until you reach 500 foot.
Retract the landing gear.

feedback_group.adviceText: Wait for speed to reach 80 knots
feedback_group.textSpeak: Wait for speed to reach 80 knots

feedback_group.adviceText: Set the flaps to 1 and disarm the spoilers.
feedback_group.textSpeak: Set the flaps to 1 and disarm the spoilers.

feedback_group.adviceText: Wait for speed to reach 100 knots
feedback_group.textSpeak: Wait for speed to reach 110 knots
Set the flaps to 0.
Tutorial completed!
